{"tid":1356070,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[轉載 最新消息] 懷疑原來係忠義想嫁禍比勝和","createTime":"2019-07-23T12:09:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-23T12:16:32.000Z","uid":161430,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"04277b921829f4d65ef650799fc13159aa4d742e","tid":1356070,"uid":161430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T12:09:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg10-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/67402112_147872582951445_5547912004745822208_n.jpg?_nc_cat=1&amp;_nc_oc=AQllEnIMbsuAZbmNrrKTbcc8EtHx-_-a87HVInNJtJtUk18jFnR4InCajKvhzdJT_i0&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg10-1.fna&amp;oh=90583aebeb89295d7c5f8989ba77cd47&amp;oe=5DE8B210\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg10-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F67402112_147872582951445_5547912004745822208_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D1%26_nc_oc%3DAQllEnIMbsuAZbmNrrKTbcc8EtHx-_-a87HVInNJtJtUk18jFnR4InCajKvhzdJT_i0%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg10-1.fna%26oh%3D90583aebeb89295d7c5f8989ba77cd47%26oe%3D5DE8B210&h=15835e4a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我都覺得奇怪，尋日開始有風聲流傳，<br />\n忠義大波不滿自己付出咁多，但關心度同酬勞都低過其他團體，<br />\n今日就即刻爆件搞何妖墳既事，<br />\n仲要專登寫住&quot;勝和字&quot;，但又寫住&quot;官黑勾結&quot;，唔覺得好怪咩？<br />\n<br />\n大家唔好比人帶風向，可能其實係忠義搞出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲惡到想嫁禍比勝和，雖然大家都係黑，但都唔好抄車"},{"pid":"ca82ffb9d1daa22de8196cabdf53f6b9b497e11e","tid":1356070,"uid":161430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T12:11:13.000Z","msg":"大波，你都陰毒呀，玩暗算"},{"pid":"c6f5c242134484016d23e8f9f6421cffa1b91016","tid":1356070,"uid":161430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T12:16:32.000Z","msg":"收唔足尾數就要咁樣玩嫁禍"}]}